OL,3,CMum launches CPR campaign after saving
OL,4,Cbaby's life
OL,6,FA mum from Wiltshire who saved her
OL,7,Fbaby's life by performing CPR is
OL,8,Fcalling for other parents to be
OL,9,Ftrained in the life-saving technique.
OL,11,FHayley Gardyj, from Melksham,
OL,12,Fsuccessfully resuscitated her newborn
OL,13,Fson Brodie after he went limp and
OL,14,Fstopped breathing during a shopping
OL,15,Ftrip.
OL,17,FShe is campaigning for every child's
OL,18,FPersonal Health Care Record - known as
OL,19,Fthe 'Red Book' - to include a QR code
OL,20,Fwhich links to a CPR training video.
