OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country,
OL,7,FHayley described the moment she
OL,8,Frealised something was wrong with her
OL,9,Fson.
OL,11,F'I knew he was gone' - Mum
OL,13,FHayley said: "We got in the car to go
OL,14,Fhome and his cry decreased massively
OL,15,Fand I thought this isn't right.
OL,17,F"I got out of the car and tried to
OL,18,Fconsole him and he was screaming. All
OL,19,Fof a sudden, he just stopped.
