OL,6,F"I looked down at him and his head had
OL,7,Fcompletely flopped back and he looked
OL,8,Fgrey, he was blue around the mouth,
OL,9,Fand I knew he was gone."
OL,11,FHayley ran to a nearby veterinary
OL,12,Fpractice with her baby and asked them
OL,13,Fto ring 999, while she desperately
OL,14,Ftried to remember the CPR training she
OL,15,Fhad received a few years ago.
OL,17,F"I put him on a chair and started CPR
OL,18,Fbut I suddenly remembered he needed to
OL,19,Fbe on a flat surface," she explained.
