OL,6,F"They took me into one of the vet's
OL,7,Fconsultation rooms and I put him on
OL,8,Fone of their tables.
OL,10,F"It was three to four minutes of
OL,11,Fconstant compressions and then the vet
OL,12,Fsaid he's got a heartbeat.
OL,14,F"The paramedics arrived and, as soon
OL,15,Fas they took over, I just collapsed."
OL,17,FBrodie was born premature, and his
OL,18,Flung had collapsed. But two years on,
OL,19,FHayley has turned this traumatic
OL,20,Fexperience into something positive.
