OL,6,FShe has been campaigning tirelessly to
OL,7,Fraise awareness of CPR training and
OL,8,Fthe QR code video in the hope it could
OL,9,Fsave others.
OL,11,F"If someone contacts me and says I
OL,12,Fsaved my baby because I saw your video
OL,13,Fthat would mean the world to me," said
OL,14,FHayley.
OL,16,F"I want to turn something that will
OL,17,Fforever haunt me into something
OL,18,Fpositive. Think how many lives could
OL,19,Fbe saved."
