OL,6,FThe contents of the 'Red Book' is
OL,7,Foverseen by a Royal College of
OL,8,FPaediatrics and Child Health panel.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the panel said:
OL,11,F"The Committee makes recommendations
OL,12,Fregarding changes to the red book as a
OL,13,Fresult of user-requested change,
OL,14,Fpolicy changes and design changes.
OL,16,F"The committee is open to considering
OL,17,Fall suggestions for content. This
OL,18,Fcampaign has been passed on to the
OL,19,Fcommittee for consideration."
